The Krypton CSharp Compiler
================================
This program is a simple Command Line compiler for the C# programming language. Faster and more
portable than the IDE Compilers.

Extra Features
================================
- KCS allows the use of custom C# makefiles 

###################################
FILE: program.cs
COMPILER: kcs.exe
DEST: a.exe
MAIN
###################################

- Command Line compiling

- Faster

